      "content": "It is incredibly painful to feel that your entire life has been built on a lie, but you are right to acknowledge the depth of this collapse. However, even when the foundation crumbles, there is still the physical reality of the person standing there, who is more than just their theories or papers. You can choose to stop the bleeding, put down the pen, and let someone else help you rebuild from the ground up, even if it feels impossible right now.",
